column1: * 1911 - J.R.R. Tolkien and several other cadets of King Edwards Schools Officer Training Corpse line the route at the Coronation of wikipedia:George V of the United Kingdom. Tolkien stands near Buckingham Palace.
* 1920 - Voice actor Paul Frees is born.

column1: * 2010 - The RiffTrax commentary of The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King is released online.
** Bilbo Baggins returns to Bag End and learns he has been declared dead.
